{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"896d5ebf0d","title":"《词六首》序","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6a621950b8","index":0,"year":1962,"month":4,"day":null,"articleId":"896d5ebf0d"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji45","name":"毛泽东全集第45卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/45-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji45":{"comments":[{"id":"682411611e","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"896d5ebf0d","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东为《词六首》在《人民文学》1962年五月号发表所写的序，后未发，改刊了另一则较短的序。"},{"id":"f11f3751b2","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"896d5ebf0d","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"1962年1月15日《人民文学》编辑部写信给毛泽东，信中说：“最近我们辑转搜寻，找到了您的几首诗词。正因为是无转搜寻到的，所以不知是否有说误，也不知您是否愿意将其发表，或者是不是还需要修改，因此抄寄一份给您，请您指示，并请注上题目和写作年月。"}],"contents":[{"id":"5cd87cd381","type":"title","text":"《词六首》序一","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"896d5ebf0d"},{"id":"682411611e","type":"paragraph","text":"这六首词，年深日久，通忘记了。《人民文学》编辑部搜集起来，要求发表，以因以付之。回忆了一下，这些词是在一九二九至一九三一年在马背上嘎成的。文采不佳，却反映了那个时期人民群众和革命战士们的心情舒快状态，作为史料，是可以的。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"896d5ebf0d"}],"page":{"id":"5e87506381","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"896d5ebf0d","start":121,"end":121}}}},"__N_SSG":true}